---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
---
<div class="w-full block justify-center items-center">
    <section class="w-full flex flex-col justify-start items-center p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center lg:w-1/2">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold"><span class="text-purple-500">Haz match</span> con tu próximo Roommate en Lima</h1>
            <p class="mt-7">¿Universidad, trabajo o nueva ciudad? En Dommies, conectamos roommates en Lima (Miraflores, San Isidro, Surco, etc) con personalidades, presupuesto, ubicación e intereses similares, para que puedas convivir en un ambiente menos conflictivo. Ah, y verificamos todos los perfiles 😊</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center items-center my-16">
            <a class="w-full flex justify-center items-center h-auto bg-purple-500 text-white shadow-lg p-2 px-4 lg:mx-5 rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd4Vwls-Jq53VHIdW-oelFDOPsUYEGybQM2POU8FXFq4hC10w/viewform" target="_blank">
                Quiero encontrar mi Roommate en Lima
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-right ml-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h11.793l-3.147-3.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l4 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L13.293 8.5H1.5A.5.5 0 0 1 1 8"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/2 flex justify-center items-center">
            <div class="flex">Síguenos</div>
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 ml-5">
                <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/message/2QBIZN45ZCPHA1?autoload=1&app_absent=0" target="_blank" aria-label="Enviar un mensaje por WhatsApp"><i class="bi bi-whatsapp cursor-pointer"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61570895938953" target="_blank" aria-label="Visitar nuestra página de Facebook"><i class="bi bi-facebook cursor-pointer"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@dommies.pro" target="_blank" aria-label="Visitar nuestra cuenta de TikTok"><i class="bi bi-tiktok cursor-pointer"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/Dommiess.pro/" target="_blank" aria-label="Visitar nuestro perfil de Instagram"><i class="bi bi-instagram cursor-pointer"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-3/5 aspect-video flex justify-center items-center mt-5">
            <img src="/Macbook-Mockup.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" 
                 class="w-full h-full object-contain">
        </div>        
    </section>
    <section class="w-full flex flex-wrap justify-evenly items-center px-5 gap-5 p-2 py-5 bg-[#8A5EE2]">
        <div class="w-40 lg:w-52 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl mb-4 font-bold">903 perfiles</h3>
            <p class="">Analizados para el entrenamiento IA</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-40 lg:w-52 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl mb-4 font-bold">71%</h3>
            <p class="">Precisión de Recomendaciones</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-40 lg:w-52 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl mb-4 font-bold">4MBTI</h3>
            <p class="">Enfoques de Personalidad MBTI</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-40 lg:w-52 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl mb-4 font-bold">100%</h3>
            <p class="">Usuarios con validación de identidad</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="w-full py-16 flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-8 lg:px-36">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
            <h1 class="w-full text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">¿Es 
            <span class="text-purple-500">Dommies</span> para ti?</h1>
            <div class="block lg:flex justify-center items-center">
                <div class="block justify-center items-center">
                    <p class="mb-5">¡Definitivamente sí, si te identificas con esto!:</p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center ml-8">
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                            <li class=""><span class="font-bold">Estudiantes universitarios</span> que buscan roommates en Lima y quieren un espacio cerca de su universidad.</li>
                            <li class=""><span class="font-bold">Jóvenes profesionales</span> listos para independizarse y compartir gastos buscando roommates en Miraflores, San Isidro, Surco, La molina, etc.</li>
                            <li>Jóvenes que <span class="font-bold">ya tienen vivienda</span> y buscan un Roommate para alquilar su habitación extra y compartir su espacio.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full flex justify-start items-center my-12">
                        <a class="w-auto flex justify-center items-center h-auto bg-white text-purple-500 shadow-lg py-3 px-5 rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd4Vwls-Jq53VHIdW-oelFDOPsUYEGybQM2POU8FXFq4hC10w/viewform" target="_blank" aria-label="">
                            Regístrarse Ahora
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-right ml-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h11.793l-3.147-3.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l4 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L13.293 8.5H1.5A.5.5 0 0 1 1 8"/>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex md:hidden lg:flex justify-center items-start">
                    <img src="/perfil.webp" alt="" class="w-full h-full">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-3/5 aspect-video">
            <img src="/perfil2.webp" alt="" class="w-full h-full">
        </div>
    </section>
</div>